        <figure id="e3001116" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figJ09/J09019.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"/>
            <caption>Glow plug</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Glow plugs are compact electric heating devices that heat the cylinders to aid cold engine starting and
            reduce exhaust emissions during warm-up. There are three glow plugs installed in each cylinder head, one for
            each cylinder.
        </para>
